Plot: In this film noir satire, a blonde bombshell takes two detectives a rough ride when they cross paths over a poolside murder. Los Angeles will never be the same again...or will it?
Title: Case File 69
Writer: Gabriel Andrade (story), Christina Y. Jun (story), Matt Mendoza (story), Jamie Miller (story), Tyler Ham Pong, Vivi Thai (story), Samia Zaidi (story)
Actors: Gabriel Andrade, Christina Y. Jun, Matt Mendoza, Tyler Ham Pong
